data.description: This CUTE Third Ward Bungalow is in such a great location and neighborhood! It has a great fenced in backyard off the patio that is perfect for grilling or hanging out. The detached two car carport has a large storage room attached to it. The Large Living Room has a welcoming bay window and the large Dining Room offers you plenty of space to use how you want. Both have hardwood floors. The Cute Kitchen has white cabinets, brick backsplash, stainless appliances and tile floors. Down the hall there are three bedrooms and two bathrooms. One of the bathrooms has a classic claw foot tub.  Located just down the street from the popular Third Ward Park, this cute  house is waiting for the buyer who wants to enjoy living close enough to downtown to enjoy but also far enough away to just enjoy the welcoming neighborhood.
